		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Tout web: &#8220;PC magazine&#8221; comme le &#8220;Christian Science Monitor&#8221;]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.chienecrase.com/?p=119" />
		<id>http://www.chienecrase.com/?p=119</id>
